surfit 2.2 changes:

Bugfixes:
	* bugfix in pnts_read function. Allows to use various separators
	* bugfix in functions nodes_in_curv and nodes_in_curv_mask
	* problem with loading modules more than one time
	* bugfix in area_save_bln - rewriting file now tuned off :)
	* bugfix in completer functional. Now it works correctly with undefined areas
	* bugfix in trend functional.

New:
	+ 64-bit platform support
	+ added pnts_abs function
	+ added surf_filter_by_mask
	+ added surf_filter_in_area
	+ added surf_filter_out_area
	+ added surf_filter_by_surf
	+ added surf_swapxy
	+ cntr_load_shp syntax extended. Now you can load contours with constant Z value
	  from shapefiles of SHPYT_ARC type.

	+ regexp and wildcards support for commands and gridding rules
	+ added new parameter to surf_load_xyz function. Allows to force binding points 
          to grid cells.
	+ new gridding rule - "contours" for smooth contours approximation and interpolation

Other changes:
	- removed curvs_load_shp, use curv_load_shp instead
	- removed areas_load_shp, use area_load_shp instead
	- removed cntrs_load_shp, use cntr_load_shp instead
	$ mask_by_surf renamed to mask_from_surf


surfit 2.1 changes:

	! new module : libsurfit_io - import/export data in various formats
 	! new module : surfit4saga - surfit plugin for SAGA-GIS

	! new library used : libjpeg-6b (libsurfit_io)
	! new library used : EasyBMP-1.03 (libsurfit_io)
	! new library used : shapelib-1.2.10 (libsurfit_io)
	! new library used : netcdf-2.5.0 (libsurfit_io)
	! new library used : zlib-1.2.3 (libglobe)

	* small bugfix with taking faults into account
	* bugfix with mask input/output to surfit datafile

	+ added input/output of GMT maps (CDF format) : surf_load_gmt and surf_save_gmt commands
	+ added input/output of GRASS maps (ASCII format) : surf_load_grass and surf_save_grass commands
	+ added input/output of ArcGIS maps (ASCII format) : surf_load_arcgis and surf_save_arcgis commands
	+ added input/output of ERSI shapfiles :
		pnts_load_shp pnts_save_shp 
		curv_load_shp curvs_load_shp curv_save_shp
		area_load_shp areas_load_shp area_save_shp
		cntr_load_shp cntrs_load_shp cntr_save_shp
	+ added anisotropy for completer
	+ added import/export of surfaces to JPEG images (export in grayscale colormap) :
		surf_load_jpg surf_save_jpg
	+ added import/export of surfaces to BMP images (export in grayscale colormap) :
		surf_load_bmp surf_save_bmp
	+ added import of surfaces from XYZ text files 
		surf_load_xyz

New examples:
	area_completer.tcl
	mask.tcl
	mask_add.tcl
	mask_ineq.tcl
	mask_surf.tcl
	mask_surf_add.tcl

New gridding rules
	+ area_completer
	+ area_completer_add
	+ mask_add
	+ mask_leq
	+ mask_geq
	+ mask_surf
	+ mask_surf_add
	+ mask_surf_leq
	+ mask_surf_geq
	+ mask_mean
	+ mask_wmean
	+ mask_completer
	+ mask_completer_add

Other new commands:
	+ surf_mask_mean
	+ surf_mask_wmean

